(19, 'What are the risks that can be covered?', '<div align="justify">\r\n<ul class="style21">\r\n    <li><strong> Perils of the seas, rivers, lakes or other navigable waters. </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Fire or explosion</strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Piracy.</strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Jettison </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> General average sacrifice, salvage charges </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Earthquake, volcanic eruption or lightning </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> War and SRCC is specifically covered </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'What are the risks that can be covered?', '<div align="justify">\r\n<ul class="style21">\r\n    <li><strong> Perils of the seas, rivers, lakes or other navigable waters. </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Fire or explosion</strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Piracy.</strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Jettison </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> General average sacrifice, salvage charges </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> Earthquake, volcanic eruption or lightning </strong></li>\r\n    <li><strong> War and SRCC is specifically covered </strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:06:26'),
(20, 'What is insured?', '<strong>Ocean Going Vessels and Coastal Vessels such as General Cargo,  Bulk Carrier, Oil Tankers, Tugs, Barges, Dredgers and even Special  Purpose Vessels like Seismographic Vessels, etc. </strong>', 'What is insured?', '<strong>Ocean Going Vessels and Coastal Vessels such as General Cargo,  Bulk Carrier, Oil Tankers, Tugs, Barges, Dredgers and even Special  Purpose Vessels like Seismographic Vessels, etc. </strong>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:07:19'),
(21, 'What cover we offer?', '<strong>Loss or damage to Hull &amp; Machinery. </strong>', 'What cover we offer?', '<strong>Loss or damage to Hull &amp; Machinery. </strong>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:07:55'),
(22, 'What is an Open Policy?', '<strong>Open Policy is usually issued for export/import shipments. It is  a continuous contract effected for a period of 12 months and renewable  automatically, whereby the insurance company agrees to provide insurance  cover to all shipments coming within the scope of the open policy. As  and when shipments are declared, certificates are issued as evidence to  the contract. </strong>', 'What is an Open Policy?', '<strong>Open Policy is usually issued for export/import shipments. It is  a continuous contract effected for a period of 12 months and renewable  automatically, whereby the insurance company agrees to provide insurance  cover to all shipments coming within the scope of the open policy. As  and when shipments are declared, certificates are issued as evidence to  the contract. </strong>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:12:28'),
(23, 'What is a Specific/Individual Policy?', '<strong>This policy is valid for a single voyage or transit. The policy  will be issued before the voyage starts. The coverage will cease  immediately upon completion of the voyage/transit. </strong>', 'What is a Specific/Individual Policy?', '<strong>This policy is valid for a single voyage or transit. The policy  will be issued before the voyage starts. The coverage will cease  immediately upon completion of the voyage/transit. </strong>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:13:26'),
(24, 'What is an Annual Policy?', '<strong>This is a twelve months policy and is issued to cover goods in transit by land within a specified agreed territory. </strong>', 'What is an Annual Policy?', '<strong>This is a twelve months policy and is issued to cover goods in transit by land within a specified agreed territory. </strong>', 1, '2014-06-07 13:13:54');
